# sync

  [页缓存回写时，导致sync阻塞的问题]()
  [](http://blog.csdn.net/chenyu105/article/details/8079338)

# 解决方案

  边解压边sync

  [pdflush进程详解](http://www.2cto.com/os/201304/206490.html)
  /proc/sys/vm/dirty_background_ratio
  /proc/sys/vm/dirty_writeback_centisecs

# httpd

  telnet 80 会导致httpd链接异常，
  致使 curl 及 nc 表现异常。

  { sleep 2; echo;echo;  } | telnet 192.168.2.44 80 2>&1 | 
  grep "Connection closed" || sleep 10

